pageContext.claim: “'People are upset, and they have a right to be. Georgia not only supported Trump in 2016, but now. This is the only State in the Deep South that went for Biden? Have they lost their minds? This is going to escalate dramatically. This is a very dangerous moment in our history. The fact that our Country is being stolen. A coup is taking place in front of our eyes, and the public can't take this anymore.' A Trump fan at Georgia Rally on @OANN Bad!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump quotes a supporter falsely saying that Biden's victory represents a "coup" in the United States.
